{"number":108,"ayahs":[{"numberInSurah":1,"arabic":" إِنَّآ أَعْطَيْنَـٰكَ ٱلْكَوْثَرَ","translation":"Indeed, We have granted you, [O Muḥammad], al-Kawthar.","transliteration":"Inna aAAtaynakaalkawthar","page":602},{"numberInSurah":2,"arabic":"فَصَلِّ لِرَبِّكَ وَٱنْحَرْ","translation":"So pray to your Lord and offer sacrifice [to Him alone].","transliteration":"Fasalli lirabbika wanhar","page":602},{"numberInSurah":3,"arabic":"إِنَّ شَانِئَكَ هُوَ ٱلْأَبْتَرُ","translation":"Indeed, your enemy is the one cut off.","transliteration":"Inna shani-aka huwa al-abtar","page":602}]}